郭桢    图  文Art and poetry created by Zhen Guo在一个没有云彩的夜晚In a night without clouds星星也不知道哪里去了Dont know the stars where to go整个天空就像一个硕大的黑锅The whole sky is a huge black pot扣在大地的上空， 伸手不见五指Buckled over the earth, reaches out and sees nothing我站在这片空荡的旷野里I stood in the empty wilderness心里寻找着昔日的香花 野草 阳光 雨露 嬉笑的伙伴，至年的爱情My heart searching for the pretty flowers, sunshine, rain, exposed laughter, the loves of youth手里提着我的记忆Holding my memory in my hand脑子里闪着星星的火光The stars are shining in my head 脚下却在不停的彷徨But under my foot I hesitate郭桢文 5/2012   图 2016